Class RentalModel

java.lang.Object
rental.cosplay.model.RentalModel
public class RentalModel extends Object
Represents a rental transaction in the cosplay rental system. Contains all rental details including customer information, costume details, rental duration, dates, and payment information.

      public RentalModel(String nama, String nomorTelp, String alamat, String kostum, String ukuran, int durasiPinjam, int harga)
      Constructs a new RentalModel for creating a rental transaction.
      Parameters:
      nama - customer name
      nomorTelp - customer phone number
      alamat - customer address
      kostum - costume ID
      ukuran - costume size
      durasiPinjam - rental duration in days
      harga - rental price per day

    • RentalModel

      public RentalModel(String idRental, String nama, String nomorTelp, String alamat, int durasiPinjam, String ukuran, int harga, String tglPinjam, String tglKembali, String status)
      Constructs a complete RentalModel with all rental information.
      Parameters:
      idRental - unique rental transaction ID
      nama - customer name
      nomorTelp - customer phone number
      alamat - customer address
      durasiPinjam - rental duration in days
      ukuran - costume size
      harga - rental price per day
      tglPinjam - rental start date
      tglKembali - expected return date
      status - rental status (e.g., "Belum Kembali", "Sudah Kembali")
